38:42.320 --> 38:44.740
Of bogeymen.

38:44.740 --> 38:48.493
And dying cultures
and deep states.

38:49.619 --> 38:53.498
And we will counter him...

38:54.624 --> 38:56.543
...too.

39:00.881 --> 39:02.716
No further questions,
Your Honors.

39:21.860 --> 39:24.863
<i>After two days
of deliberation,</i>

39:24.863 --> 39:27.032
<i>the verdict is in.</i>

39:27.032 --> 39:29.117
<i>The world waits nervously
as the justices</i>

39:29.117 --> 39:31.161
