53:10.187 --> 53:13.441
Our reward for being
in this absurd life.

53:13.441 --> 53:15.526
To be seen.

53:17.236 --> 53:19.238
How simple.

53:20.615 --> 53:22.617
What else is there...

53:24.076 --> 53:26.287
