53:59.195 --> 54:02.573
- Hi.
- Hi.

54:09.872 --> 54:11.874
I'm sorry.

54:35.147 --> 54:37.108
Come on, love,
we're going to be late.

54:38.109 --> 54:41.696
Says the woman whose
been in the shower for an hour.

54:43.990 --> 54:45.658
Yeah?

54:45.658 --> 54:47.368
<i>Bonjour,
Madame Morris, I have</i>

54:47.368 --> 54:50.037
<i>a Congresswoman Handelman
for you.</i>

54:50.037 --> 54:51.789
<i>Agent Morris.</i>

54:51.789 --> 54:53.791
Liz.

54:53.791 --> 54:55.793
<i>It's been a long time.</i>

54:55.793 --> 54:57.753
<i>A long road.</i>

54:57.753 --> 55:00.589
<i>But I'm calling to say...
good work.</i>

55:00.589 --> 55:02.258
What?

55:02.258 --> 55:04.552
<i>On bringing Hitler to justice.</i>

55:04.552 --> 55:06.971
<i>We would like to honor you</i>

55:06.971 --> 55:09.056
<i>with the Congressional
Gold Medal.</i>

55:10.224 --> 55:12.226
<i>I was calling to tell you
the good news.</i>

55:17.982 --> 55:20.192
It was me.

55:21.652 --> 55:24.071
I shot him. I shot Prentz.
It was me.

55:28.284 --> 55:31.829
<i>We can't wait
to honor you in D.C.</i>

55:31.829 --> 55:34.373
<i>You're a hero, Millie.</i>

55:34.373 --> 55:36.917
<i>The world needs heroes.</i>

55:55.311 --> 55:57.146
Oh, hey.

55:57.146 --> 55:59.065
Come on, love. We can't be late.

55:59.065 --> 56:01.150
Hmm?

56:14.205 --> 56:16.123
Mazel tov!

56:23.380 --> 56:25.299
<i>Love ♪</i>

56:25.299 --> 56:28.511
<i>♪ Love will keep us together...</i>

56:28.511 --> 56:31.555
I am shocked that you didn't
bring a plus one.

56:31.555 --> 56:33.099
Of course I did.

56:35.601 --> 56:36.894
