<i>♪ Be there to share forever...</i>

57:09.301 --> 57:10.845
How do you drink these?

57:10.845 --> 57:13.013
<i>♪ Love will keep us together...</i>

57:13.013 --> 57:15.266
I am not dancing alone.

57:15.266 --> 57:16.976
- You're coming with me.
- All right.

57:16.976 --> 57:18.686
- Who is that? Hi.
