57:43.127 --> 57:45.421
Look, she would be, um...

57:45.421 --> 57:47.339
proud.

57:47.339 --> 57:49.049
Of who you became.

57:49.049 --> 57:50.718
Of who you are.

57:50.718 --> 57:53.095
Mm.

57:53.095 --> 57:55.973
I've known a lot of monsters, Jonah.

57:55.973 --> 57:58.767
You're not one of them.

57:58.767 --> 58:00.936
