1:02:45.596 --> 1:02:47.097
To new beginnings.

1:02:48.932 --> 1:02:50.517
<i>L'chaim.</i>

1:03:05.991 --> 1:03:08.202
- Here you are, sir.
- <i>Danke.</i>
